      "title": "E236｜99%的作业都是AI写的：当代名校生眼里，大学还剩下什么？",
      "url": "https://aphid.fireside.fm/d/1437767933/f0f20376-8faf-4940-b920-84af6c734e2d/b066c769-00d2-4341-bf61-a82bca4181e4.mp3",
